title: US Census, Vermont by Tracts, Demographics 2000
name: US Census, Vermont by Tracts, Demographics 2000
description:
This is the Decennial United States Government Census from the year 2000. This data is shown at the Census Tract level for Each State in the United States of America. Census Tracts are more detailed than counties or states, but less detailed than Census Blocks or Block Groups. Each of these Census Datasets includes detailed information on the general population, including Sex, Age, Race, Income, Housing, School Enrollment, and other categories. Enjoy the US Census. 

Original Source: US Census  www.Census.gov
